{"tid":383262,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"《出貓特攻隊》真有其事, 中國出貓機構利用時差作弊","createTime":"2017-09-01T10:35:29.000Z","updateTime":"2017-09-10T14:18:28.000Z","uid":134071,"like":72,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"2665e5e75793a69d3cfb923cd35bb7dc1d5c03c8","tid":383262,"uid":134071,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-01T10:35:29.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-small;\"><a href=\"http://www.hk01.com/%E9%9B%BB%E5%BD%B1/111975/-%E5%87%BA%E8%B2%93%E7%89%B9%E6%94%BB%E9%9A%8A-%E6%87%B6%E4%BA%BA%E5%8C%85-%E4%BD%9C%E5%BC%8A%E6%A9%8B%E6%AE%B5%E7%9C%9F%E6%9C%89%E5%85%B6%E4%BA%8B-%E4%B8%AD%E5%9C%8B%E8%80%83%E7%94%9F%E7%A5%9E%E9%82%84%E5%8E%9F\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.hk01.com%2F%25E9%259B%25BB%25E5%25BD%25B1%2F111975%2F-%25E5%2587%25BA%25E8%25B2%2593%25E7%2589%25B9%25E6%2594%25BB%25E9%259A%258A-%25E6%2587%25B6%25E4%25BA%25BA%25E5%258C%2585-%25E4%25BD%259C%25E5%25BC%258A%25E6%25A9%258B%25E6%25AE%25B5%25E7%259C%259F%25E6%259C%2589%25E5%2585%25B6%25E4%25BA%258B-%25E4%25B8%25AD%25E5%259C%258B%25E8%2580%2583%25E7%2594%259F%25E7%25A5%259E%25E9%2582%2584%25E5%258E%259F&d=rMgaN5TqaeNk4%2FQu35GHkDA5unq%2FSd9ZKvr75NUD1%2F0%3D&h=936abb6c\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.hk01.com/%E9%9B%BB%E5%BD%B1/111975/-%E5%87%BA%E8%B2%93%E7%89%B9%E6%94%BB%E9%9A%8A-%E6%87%B6%E4%BA%BA%E5%8C%85-%E4%BD%9C%E5%BC%8A%E6%A9%8B%E6%AE%B5%E7%9C%9F%E6%9C%89%E5%85%B6%E4%BA%8B-%E4%B8%AD%E5%9C%8B%E8%80%83%E7%94%9F%E7%A5%9E%E9%82%84%E5%8E%9F</a></span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n不要以為如此誇張的出貓方式只在泰國發生，<strong>中國同樣有類似的情況。而且更似《出貓特攻隊》的劇情</strong>！在世界不同地方都設立考場的SAT（美國高考）早前便發現有中國考生出貓。據《華盛頓郵報》報導，去年10月在泰國曼谷的SAT考場，一名考官發現有10位中國考生不僅坐在同一排，而且准考證也是連號，有理由相信是有組織的機構，通過提早獲得答案，把答案交予考生。<strong>而該考官指相信這些機構一定從中大賺，而且有理由相信除了泰國外，其他同時區的SAT考場亦有類似事件沒被揭發。</strong><br />\n<br />\n據知，其中一名中國女考生把手提電話藏於衣服口袋，考前聲稱已交由母親保管，而由於SAT的考官不會對考生搜身，所以私藏手機他們無法知曉。結果該名女考生因在考試期偷看手機而人贓並獲，考官檢查手機發現內裡有當天試題的正確答案。而後來她亦供稱，這些答案都是來自當天稍早時候，於澳洲舉行的SAT考試。<strong>而事件影響所及，美國SAT主辦方為了防止作弊，在今年6月的考試中更直接取消了美國本地以外的所有考場，中國可謂「一個累全家」，其他國家也備受牽連。</strong>"},{"pid":"acc15954fc38c448e0c27d87dad368b356058c49","tid":383262,"uid":51200,"like":1,"dislike":3,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-01T11:40:54.000Z","msg":"用同一份卷考係為咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9e7c751981711169a471cc785bc6cc715560a1a6","tid":383262,"uid":35637,"like":27,"dislike":0,"score":27,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-01T11:42:24.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>用同一份卷考係為咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n公平<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n唔係就會有人易d 拎a"},{"pid":"eaa1bdd68fe8d667eaa12471bcba0fffadd4bf13","tid":383262,"uid":73748,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-01T11:43:46.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>用同一份卷考係為咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n同一個考試，無理由兩份卷"},{"pid":"b29067234a1898d0f92e3d7c8a0b0f56ccb09926","tid":383262,"uid":85819,"like":19,"dislike":0,"score":19,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-01T11:44:32.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"4282127c4f0992e1f3d423ed6b9e8d222021dd7e","tid":383262,"uid":22974,"like":24,"dislike":0,"score":24,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-01T11:47:04.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"25bccb96eaeaf111979e212a82eadfb588546a25","tid":383262,"uid":89683,"like":1,"dislike":19,"score":-18,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-01T12:11:52.000Z","msg":"全球同一時間考唔得咩？<br />\n有d地區夜晚考，有d地區朝早考"},{"pid":"591061cdfec7248e1c9022612ff85ff1fc6880bd","tid":383262,"uid":9732,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-01T12:14:34.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>全球同一時間考唔得咩？<br />\n有d地區夜晚考，有d地區朝早考</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"283104825d53d61a6e7ecfdc1dd94b9167d3c9dc","tid":383262,"uid":89683,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-01T12:17:23.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>全球同一時間考唔得咩？<br />\n有d地區夜晚考，有d地區朝早考</bloc